Dear Sir/Madam,
My FWO promotor (Prof. Dr. Hans Van Winckel) and I were recently contacted to upload the data
management plan for our FWO project (1239522N). I would like to inform that we have postponed
this project for two years and that I will start this project in October 2023. This is the reason why
we did not upload any data management plan for this year. Please let me know if its okay to pro-
ceedlikethisorifIhavetofillinanyotherformtoinformaboutthepostponementoftheFWOproject.
Thanks for your cooperation,
Kind regards,
Shreeya Shetye
